@16:51 - ROC called regarding CO2 adjusted PH Lolo, filters 1/2 Lo, and settled water Lolo alarms.  Low lifts had interlocked due to CO2 pH alarms.  Directed ROC Christian to Ack/reset alarm, and place the filter #1 and #2 effluent valves to manual close in order to allow the filters / conduit to recover. Will check SCADA shortly.  

